{
  "stem": "5758.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had a-- our very close friend of my parents, a neighbor of ours, Miss Schiff, Erna Schiff, and our family.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it-- it was a family function at home, not a bar mitzvah like you had and-- where you invite thousands of people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at that time, I felt left out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My oldest brother-- don't forget, my oldest brother, he was born 1913 on the 5th of April.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was-- 1913, he was eight-- eight years, is it?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was born 1921.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yes, so it's eight years older than me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So when you are of the age of, let's say, 13 and he's 21, he's a man, nearly.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He went out with girls.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And naturally, I was too young.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] My middle brother, Eric, was two years older than I am.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was born in-- in 1920-- 1919.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] With the oldest brother I didn't have too much in common.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Even with my two-year older brother, I didn't have really-- I was-- I felt left out, because what they were doing I couldn't do.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because when you are that young, you're really the baby of the family.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In fact, I must say I looked extremely young, much younger than my years.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So when I was, let's say, 15, and-- and I saw some of my school friends going out with girls, I couldn't because I was-- I looked like 12.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I had a little bit of a complex maybe because of it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I always looked young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Today I'm very happy because I-- I-- I'm--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I still look young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The--",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
